node.text:
A new auction has just rolled into town and it's going to be epic! @RRRawlings is going to be at the @MapleBrothersAuction here in Dallas on August 6th and 7th and bringing our 1960 Thunderbird to the auction block. 

Tap the link in our bio or head to MapleBrothersAuction.com/RichardRawlings to check out all the classics up for sale and register to bid. See you there!

#GasMonkeyGarage #GasMonkey #RichardRawlings

node.title: A new auction has just rolled into town! @MapleBrothersAuction

node.text:
By Vets, for Vets. Since we met @AmericanWarriorGarage on #GarageRehab, they've become like family to us. The work they do isn't easy. By entering to win this 1962 Thunderbird, you are supporting American Warrior Garage to continue to help Veterans get back on their feet. Help them help others. 

Want a chance to win this 1962 Thunderbird? Check out ➡️ https://bit.ly/62THUNDERBIRD-GIVEAWAY LINK IN BIO 

#GasMonkeyGarage #GasMonkey #RichardRawlings #FastNLoud

node.title: YOU could WIN a 1962 Thunderbird from American Warrior Garage!

node.text:
It’s a wrap! This year's One Lap of America is over! Did we win?... Nope 😅 Did we push a 20-year-old 911 GT2 through its paces and finish right side up? Yep!🙌 

Big thanks to all that that helped us get the GT2 through 3800+ miles, 12 events, and 16 different states. Thanks to all of you for following! Til next year.

Huge thanks to all of his sponsors:
@Fabspeed_Motorsport @dynamat_official @levrack @bbkperformance @girodisc @Amspecgroup @Brenspeed @petrolheadonism.club @restoreamusclecar @musclecarsoftexas @domromphoto @turbo_max_wylie @ebcbrakesoffical @ohlinsusa @ohlinsauto @hotrodz_dallas @lonestarbrothers @gasmonkeygarage @RRRawlings

node.text:
Help Richard Now ➡️ https://bit.ly/HELP-RICHARD​ 

Guys, we need your help with Richard. He just hasn't been himself since... well you know. We've seen the comments and well, they couldn't have been more spot on. Beer time? It's past that. Burnouts? Boring. Richard simply has lost his motor and we need YOU to help him get it back. Please head over now to bit.ly/HELP-RICHARD to find out you can help. 

We can't thank y'all enough.

#HelpRichard #GasMonkeyGarage #RichardRawlings #GasMonkey

node.text:
With two buildings packed with classic cars, we couldn't fit everything that we wanted to show off in 1 video! What exactly is going on inside #Gas#MonkeyGarage?! Watch as @RRRawlings heads next door and gives an exclusive tour of the Monkey Trap and his private collection. 

Missed part 1? Head over to our YouTube Channel now (link in bio) to watch it now!

#GasMonkey #RichardRawlings #FastNLoud #Ford #Mustang #Americanmuscle #Chevy #Chevrolet #Dodge #Mopar #HotRod #ClassicCars #VintageCars #RatRod #ClassicCar #Carporn

node.text:
Gather around for story time! We have a ton of kickass cars in our garage and this 1951 Ford Club Coupe was Phipp's Dad's car and it's got one helluva story!

It was bought back in '56 when Phipps Sr. got married and he immediately hot-rodded it by putting in a Cadillac 390 engine. Since then, it's been through 3 of 'em!

During the life of the car, all 3 kids were taken to the hospital to be born in it. When it came time for those kids to learn how to drive, Mr. Phipps took it apart to "get painted". It sat in pieces for 15 years, so that those new drivers wouldn't wreck it 😂

Having a car like this around Dallas, you get recognized in it! Rumor has it, before Richard Rawlings moved GMG into the shop behind Phipps automotive, the head monkey came across it and tried to buy it! 

What do you you think of this rad 1951 Ford Club Coupe?
